{"tid":48440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（無知？）港女業主：好開心架，可以「立食」","createTime":"2016-12-21T05:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T06:17:01.000Z","uid":29314,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b299d4cca4b460e979db87bafba6f1de7d182de4","tid":48440,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:38:05.000Z","msg":"港台最新播出嘅《鏗鏘集》，迷你單位做Topic，第一個Case，就已充分解釋點解地產商樂於推出劏盤。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「好開心架，如果早啲嘅話，呢度有啲陽光射入嚟，你就可以喺度『立食』埋」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n呢位業主，能夠將「屋企冇位放餐枱」，換概念成有格調嘅「立食」；他朝有一日，屋企連床都唔夠位放，大可以同人講，「我呢啲唔係叫冇位，係小矮人主題概念房」。<br />\n<br />\n知足常樂，心中富有大概就係呢啲。"},{"pid":"9350d079bf38a9048b32a163a2e58aa1e40cb4bd","tid":48440,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20161221/large/1482297963_c752.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161221%2Flarge%2F1482297963_c752.jpg&h=41e12ee9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce6a1fc27face08501e9a86dec77c8af443713e9","tid":48440,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:39:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20161221/large/1482298030_1e17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161221%2Flarge%2F1482298030_1e17.jpg&h=082f31e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f2c98951a26931d2d21a7895626bbbd1036891a","tid":48440,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:40:24.000Z","msg":"《鏗鏘集》迷你生活：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4TDnH-wPbrc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4TDnH-wPbrc&d=OmBJcyTWCAlw5rhpG6lzZ0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=441fd30d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4TDnH-wPbrc</a>"},{"pid":"746f76078adcc32ff960d925fc8387c6ce390beb","tid":